        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            55,
            134,
            144,
            149
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $\\frac{3}{2}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            157,
            198,
            183
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{(1 + \\cos x)\\ln(1 + x)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{\\ln(1 + x)} = \\frac{1}{2}\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{3\\sin x + x^2\\cos\\frac{1}{x}}{x}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            193,
            811,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\frac {1}{2} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(3 \\frac {\\sin x}{x} + x \\cos \\frac {1}{x}\\right) = \\frac {3}{2}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            357,
            247,
            650,
            275
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $(-2,4)$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            282,
            235,
            297
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为幂级数 $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}na_n(x - 1)^{n + 1}$ 的收敛半径与 $\\sum_{n = 0}^{\\infty}a_{n}x^{n}$ 的收敛半径相同，",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            305,
            721,
            337
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所以 $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}na_n(x - 1)^{n + 1}$ 的收敛半径为 $R = 3$ ，故所求收敛区间为 $-3 < x - 1 < 3$ ，即 $(-2,4)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            343,
            828,
            374
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 $y = -x + \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            380,
            287,
            403
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 对数螺线的参数方程为 $\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l}x = \\mathrm{e}^{\\theta}\\cos \\theta ,\\\\ y = \\mathrm{e}^{\\theta}\\sin \\theta . \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            409,
            456,
            446
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{2}$ 时， $(x, y) = (0, \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}})$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            453,
            361,
            481
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{dy} / \\mathrm{d}\\theta}{\\mathrm{dx} / \\mathrm{d}\\theta} = \\frac{\\cos\\theta + \\sin\\theta}{\\cos\\theta - \\sin\\theta},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right|_{\\theta = \\frac{\\pi}{2}} = -1,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            489,
            510,
            522
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故所求切线的直角坐标方程为 $y - \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}} = -x$ ，或 $y = -x + \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{2}}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            529,
            609,
            551
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 -3.",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            558,
            200,
            571
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】方法一 因为 $B \\neq O$ 且 $AB = O$ ，所以方程组 $AX = 0$ 有非零解，",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            578,
            685,
            593
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $|\\mathbf{A}| = 0$ ，而由 $|\\mathbf{A}| = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc}1 & 2 & -2\\\\ 4 & t & 3\\\\ 3 & -1 & 1 \\end{array} \\right| = 7t + 21 = 0$ ，得 $t = -3$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            600,
            659,
            656
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二 由 $\\mathbf{AB} = \\mathbf{O}$ 得 $r(\\mathbf{A}) + r(\\mathbf{B})\\leqslant 3$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            663,
            442,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $\\pmb{B} \\neq \\pmb{0}$ 得 $r(\\pmb{B}) \\geqslant 1$ ，于是 $r(\\mathbf{A}) \\leqslant 2 < 3$ ，故 $|\\mathbf{A}| = 0$ ，解得 $t = -3$ .",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            684,
            681,
            699
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5)【答案】 $\\frac{2}{5}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            706,
            196,
            733
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】令 $A_{1} = \\{$ 第一个人取黄球 $\\}$ , $A_{2} = \\{$ 第一个人取白球 $\\}$ , $B = \\{$ 第二个人取黄球 $\\}$ ,",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            742,
            795,
            757
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nP \\left(A _ {1}\\right) = \\frac {2}{5}, \\quad P \\left(A _ {2}\\right) = \\frac {3}{5}, \\quad P \\left(B \\mid A _ {1}\\right) = \\frac {1 9}{4 9}, \\quad P \\left(B \\mid A _ {2}\\right) = \\frac {2 0}{4 9},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            216,
            766,
            799,
            792
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $P(B) = P(A_{1})P(B\\mid A_{1}) + P(A_{2})P(B\\mid A_{2})$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            800,
            502,
            814
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\frac {2}{5} \\times \\frac {1 9}{4 9} + \\frac {3}{5} \\times \\frac {2 0}{4 9} = \\frac {2}{5}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            165,
            822,
            398,
            849
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            53,
            857,
            140,
            872
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（1）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            878,
            198,
            893
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $\\lim_{\\substack{x\\to 0\\\\ y = x}}f(x,y) = \\frac{1}{2}\\neq \\lim_{\\substack{x\\to 0\\\\ y = -x}}f(x,y) = -\\frac{1}{2}$ ，所以 $f(x,y)$ 在(0，0）处不连续；",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            901,
            797,
            936
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x,0) - f(0,0)}{x - 0} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{0}{x} = 0$ 得 $f_{x}^{\\prime}(0,0) = 0$ ，同理 $f_{y}^{\\prime}(0,0) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            73,
            708,
            100
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "即 $f(x,y)$ 在 $(0,0)$ 处可偏导，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            110,
            419,
            125
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            132,
            210,
            147
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $f^{\\prime}(x) < 0$ 得 $f(x)$ 为单调减函数，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            154,
            471,
            171
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $S_{1} = \\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x > \\int_{a}^{b}f(b)\\mathrm{d}x = f(b)(b - a) = S_{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            177,
            564,
            204
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $f''(x) > 0$ 得 $f(x)$ 为凹函数，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            211,
            392,
            228
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $S_{1} = \\int_{a}^{b}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x <   \\frac{1}{2} [f(a) + f(b)](b - a) = S_{3}$ ，即 $S_{2} <   S_{1} <   S_{3}$ ，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            236,
            789,
            264
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 （A).",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            273,
            212,
            289
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由周期函数定积分的平移性质得",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            295,
            423,
            311
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} F (x) = \\int_ {- \\pi} ^ {\\pi} \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} \\sin t \\mathrm {d} t = \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} [ \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} \\sin t + \\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin (- t)} \\sin (- t) ] \\mathrm {d} t \\\\ = \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\left(\\mathrm {e} ^ {\\sin t} - \\mathrm {e} ^ {- \\sin t}\\right) \\sin t \\mathrm {d} t, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            204,
            318,
            675,
            381
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $t \\in [0, \\pi]$ 时， $(\\mathrm{e}^{\\sin t} - \\mathrm{e}^{-\\sin t})\\sin t \\geqslant 0$ ，则 $F(x) > 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            388,
            551,
            405
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $F(x)$ 为正常数，应选（A）.",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            413,
            334,
            428
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            435,
            212,
            450
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】三条直线交于一点的充分必要条件是方程组 $\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} a_{1}x + b_{1}y = -c_{1}, \\\\ a_{2}x + b_{2}y = -c_{2}, \\\\ a_{3}x + b_{3}y = -c_{3} \\end{array} \\right.$ 有唯一解，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            457,
            770,
            520
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "即 $r(\\mathbf{A}) = r(\\overline{\\mathbf{A}}) = 2$ ，其中 $\\mathbf{A} = \\begin{pmatrix} a_1 & b_1 \\\\ a_2 & b_2 \\\\ a_3 & b_3 \\end{pmatrix}, \\overline{\\mathbf{A}} = \\begin{pmatrix} a_1 & b_1 & -c_1 \\\\ a_2 & b_2 & -c_2 \\\\ a_3 & b_3 & -c_3 \\end{pmatrix}$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            528,
            642,
            590
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2},\\alpha_{3}$ 线性相关，而 $\\alpha_{1},\\alpha_{2}$ 线性无关，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            598,
            533,
            614
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            621,
            212,
            634
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 已知 $D(X) = 4$ ， $D(Y) = 2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            643,
            413,
            658
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $X, Y$ 相互独立，所以 $D(3X - 2Y) = 9D(X) + 4D(Y) = 36 + 8 = 44$ ，应选(D).三、",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            665,
            789,
            702
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】 平面曲线 $\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} y^{2} = 2z, \\\\ x = 0 \\end{array} \\right.$ 绕 $z$ 轴旋转一周形成的曲面为 $\\Sigma: x^{2} + y^{2} = 2z$ ",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            710,
            716,
            746
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $\\Omega = \\{(x,y,z) \\mid (x,y) \\in D_z, 0 \\leqslant z \\leqslant 8\\}$ ，其中 $D_z = \\{(x,y) \\mid x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant 2z\\}$ ，",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            753,
            791,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $I = \\iiint_{\\Omega}(x^{2} + y^{2})\\mathrm{d}v = \\int_{0}^{8}\\mathrm{d}z\\iint_{D_{z}}(x^{2} + y^{2})\\mathrm{d}x\\mathrm{d}y = 2\\pi \\int_{0}^{8}\\mathrm{d}z\\int_{0}^{\\sqrt{2z}}r^{3}\\mathrm{d}r$ ",
        "bbox": [
            95,
            778,
            669,
            816
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {8} z ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} z = \\frac {1 0 2 4 \\pi}{3}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            154,
            821,
            347,
            849
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【解】 方法一",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            858,
            219,
            872
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $C:\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}x = \\cos t,\\\\ y = \\sin t,\\\\ z = 2 - \\cos t + \\sin t \\end{array} \\right.$ （起点 $t = 2\\pi$ ，终点 $t = 0$ )，则",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            881,
            568,
            940
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {C} (z - y) \\mathrm {d} x + (x - z) \\mathrm {d} y + (x - y) \\mathrm {d} z \\\\ = \\int_ {2 \\pi} ^ {0} (2 - \\cos t) (- \\sin t) d t + (2 \\cos t - 2 - \\sin t) \\cos t d t + (\\cos t - \\sin t) (\\sin t + \\cos t) d t \\\\ = \\int_ {2 \\pi} ^ {0} (3 \\cos^ {2} t - \\sin^ {2} t - 2 \\sin t - 2 \\cos t) d t \\\\ = - 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\cos^ {2} t d t + \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\sin^ {2} t d t = - 1 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\cos^ {2} t d t + 4 \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\sin^ {2} t d t \\\\ = - 8 \\times \\frac {1}{2} \\times \\frac {\\pi}{2} = - 2 \\pi . \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            82,
            71,
            814,
            242
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            78,
            251,
            138,
            266
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设 $C$ 所在的截口平面块为 $\\Sigma$ ，方向向下，",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            272,
            404,
            287
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "取 $n = \\{-1, 1, -1\\}$ , 方向余弦为 $\\cos \\alpha = -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}, \\cos \\beta = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}, \\cos \\gamma = -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}$ , 则",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            295,
            721,
            327
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {C} (z - y) \\mathrm {d} x + (x - z) \\mathrm {d} y + (x - y) \\mathrm {d} z = \\frac {1}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\left| \\begin{array}{c c c} - 1 & 1 & - 1 \\\\ \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial x} & \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial y} & \\frac {\\partial}{\\partial z} \\\\ z - y & x - z & x - y \\end{array} \\right| \\mathrm {d} S = - \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {\\Sigma} \\mathrm {d} S \\\\ = - \\frac {2}{\\sqrt {3}} \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} \\sqrt {1 + \\left(\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial x}\\right) ^ {2} + \\left(\\frac {\\partial z}{\\partial y}\\right) ^ {2}} d x d y \\\\ = - 2 \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant 1} d x d y = - 2 \\pi . \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            334,
            799,
            496
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【解】 由题意得",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            499,
            216,
            514
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\mathrm {d} x}{\\mathrm {d} t} = k x (N - x), \\\\ x (0) = x _ {0}, \\end{array} \\right.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            415,
            522,
            584,
            573
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}x}{x(N - x)} = k\\mathrm{d}t$ 得 $\\frac{1}{N}\\ln \\frac{x}{N - x} = kt + C,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            580,
            450,
            609
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $x(0) = x_0$ 得 $C = \\frac{1}{N}\\ln \\frac{x_0}{N - x_0}$ ，故 $x(t) = \\frac{Nx_0\\mathrm{e}^{kNt}}{N - x_0 + x_0\\mathrm{e}^{kNt}}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            618,
            613,
            650
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            45,
            656,
            76,
            670
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】曲面 $z = x^{2} + y^{2}$ 在点 $(1, - 2,5)$ 的法向量为",
        "bbox": [
            45,
            677,
            518,
            692
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\boldsymbol {n} = \\left\\{2 x, 2 y, - 1 \\right\\} _ {(1, - 2, 5)} = \\left\\{2, - 4, - 1 \\right\\},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            326,
            701,
            671,
            715
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "即平面 $\\pi$ 的法向量为 $n = \\{2, -4, -1\\}$ ，则平面 $\\pi$ 的方程为",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            721,
            570,
            735
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\pi : 2(x - 1) - 4(y + 2) - (z - 5) = 0$ ，即 $\\pi : 2x - 4y - z - 5 = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            742,
            623,
            756
        ],
